race.comment: HOT SHOT ETHICS (8) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Bulli in a handy 26.19 beating Vaya Con Dios. Looks the one to beat. FREIGHT EXPRESS (3) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (25.35) at this track. Solid record here at this trip including six wins. Boasts two wins from three starts out of this box. Will give a great sight again. EUREKA MAC (1) was a little disappointing last start at Bulli when 4th (26.60) over 472m. Has won here at this journey. Has ability and can measure up. ZIPPER TRAIN (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.
